description.html:
Dance into the New Year with stacked lineups, historic architecture, and a vibe that goes from midnight madness to day-one bliss. Expect an immersive experience with state-of-the-art production, 10-point sound, and visual elements that transform the station into a full-scale celebration.

 

 

NYE — Dec 31
Bonobo (3-hour set) + More
A full-tilt countdown throwdown to close out the year in style.

 

 

NYD — Jan 1
Âme (Live) • Colyn • Jimi Jules • Marsh
A melodic daytime journey to start the year with intention and sunshine energy.

 

 

Single-day and two-day passes available.
